<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="death-n">death <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /deθ/    美 /deθ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] &amp; [C] 死；死亡</strong></h4>
<p>反  birth： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>deaths from</strong> car crashes 
车祸死亡人数</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>burn</strong> / <strong>starve to death</strong>
烧死/饿死</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Last night’s TV news said that by then the death of the missing people had not been proved yet.  
昨晚电视新闻报道，到那时为止失踪人员生死未卜。</p><footer>2010 湖北</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 灭亡；毁灭：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The latest booming is <strong>the death of</strong> all our hopes. 
最近的爆炸事件使我们所有的希望都化为乌有。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-bored-scared-frightened-to-death">be bored / scared / frightened to death</h3>
<p>1.<strong>无聊得 / 怕得要死：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was scared to death of what might happen next.
她对接下来可能发生的事怕得要死。</p></div></div>